it was important that we...

00:47.515 --> 00:48.747
we focus on the realism.

00:48.749 --> 00:51.650
Realism, very important.

00:51.652 --> 00:54.219
Having recently
come off a difficult shoot,

00:54.221 --> 00:56.188
it must be nice
to now be closer to home,

00:56.190 --> 00:58.223
to family.

00:58.225 --> 01:01.193
Yeah, well,
France was a challenge.

01:01.195 --> 01:03.295
We always knew it would be.

01:03.297 --> 01:04.495
I think it's safe to say

01:04.498 --> 01:06.165
that at this point
in your career,

01:06.166 --> 01:07.833
your fans know you have
a true passion for racing,

01:07.835 --> 01:09.134
for what you drive.

01:09.136 --> 01:10.536
Talk a little about
what drives you.

